commentAnnotations.text: The C-SSRS will be administered to all ongoing subjects at all remaining scheduled visits in Run In and Blinded treatments, and Rescue weeks 0, 8, 12, 16, and up to and including the EOT/ET and/or the EOS visit.
For Taiwan only: Similar to China, other countries in Asia... will adopt the same changes as those proposed for China in Amendment 3 to monitor the risk of hepatitis B reactivation.
These changes are in effect for China only: Subjects who are HBsAg negative, HBcAb positive, and HBsAb positive at Screening will have reflex testing for HBV DNA.

Defined medicated topical therapy as a topical product that contains an active pharmaceutical ingredient indicated for the treatment of AD (irrespective of whether it is an OTC or prescribed product).
